{
  "stem": "21582.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One of the first hidden schools, the ogrodek, that had a more structured academic program, was in a garden.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There wasn't-- well, first maybe, if I may jump a little bit back, back up a little bit-- I did not point out that one of the things that occurred rather early after the invasion was that Jewish people were restricted from living in certain areas.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On our street, there was an estate that I guess was vacated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it had-- it had-- a-- it was rather large, and it was wooded.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had trees.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And inside that-- that area, there was a little building, and that was the school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is also one of the things that just stands out in my memory as such an important, such a nurturing time, because, well, the teachers were so remarkable.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were so kind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They-- they even gave us plots for us to grow vegetables, to grow flowers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was a place where we could really laugh and be children and played games, lots of ballgames, art, literature was shared with such-- with such affection, with such kindness.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that, too, was stopped after a short time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These teachers are so vivid in my mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Each one was like a parent to me, a parent, an educator in the noblest, noblest sense.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that, too, stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As I'm thinking about it, I remember them reading to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember that instilling that love for literature, that-- that it was more than pages, that these were expressions that sprang from the soul.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that was very precious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That, too, as I said, was-- was stopped, and I don't know exactly the circumstances.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sure that there were lots that I cannot think of right now.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
